						<summary>

						<p>This records a similar gift of gold for burning a lamp in the Kūḍal-Āḻvār temple by Aiyyaṉ Vīramādēviyār of Pūṅguṉṟam (another) queen of <hi rend="bold">Mummuḍichchōḻa-Perumāḷ.</hi> It is quite likely that this donor was the same as <hi rend="bold">Vīramādēviyār a queen of Rājēndra-Chōḷa.</hi> (<hi rend="italic">M.E.R.</hi> No. 260 of 1915).</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
